Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.69,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, when we were little, \NManaka and I got lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.27,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to go look for coral, so we went to the far edge of the village,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.00,0:00:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but then we became so preoccupied with our search that we got lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.94,0:00:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When we got hungry and exhausted,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,right when we were about to cry,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.79,0:00:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who came to our rescue
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.43,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Without saying a word,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:43.00,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he took us by the hands and led us home.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.76,0:00:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.82,0:00:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can vividly{:3} recall the way his eyes were focused straight ahead
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way he held my hand.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.95,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.37,0:01:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,when I heard that Hikari \Nhad found Manaka,{linebreak for readability}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.87,0:01:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't all that surprised.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:04.45,0:01:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I knew somewhere in my heart that it was bound to happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.57,0:01:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And from that same place in my heart,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.49,0:01:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that if {\i1}anyone{\i0} could find her, it would be Hikari.
