Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.86,0:03:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,given her rate of recovery, \Ntaking care of her here should be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.30,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.74,0:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've been closely examining her since yesterday,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.76,0:03:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and in my professional opinion, \Nshe's quite healthy.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Her brain waves are normal too.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.66,0:03:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on you and Isaki{-kun}{'s} waking up recently,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,she should wake up soon as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you, Akari?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all to worry about!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Ena'll probably grow back, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.44,0:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm just glad Manaka's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad too?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You little—Oh, right.{we've always used closed emdashes as far as i know, so closed}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, Chisaki... thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so lively.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{replace}Up your butt{Kancho}!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You fool! Like I'd keep \Nfalling for the same attack!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.80,0:03:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With these two around, \NI'm positive she'll wake up in no time.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Behold my special move,\N the {replace}Butt Counterattack{Kancho Reversal}!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wh-What are you...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{replace}Butt Counter-Counterattack!{Kancho-Reversal Reversal}!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.71,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari must be very happy \Nnow that Manaka is back.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for all your help.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.11,0:04:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiradaira{-kun},
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.76,0:04:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,feel free to hand in your nurse's{training} log\N by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.10,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.79,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time seeing you in your new uniform. It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost didn't recognize you.{looks more like a cook}{ikr}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.32,0:04:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't gotten used to it yet either.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It still feels like I'm just playing dress-up.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're here, \Nwant to have some tea?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose I could \Nimpose on you a bit more.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,hurry and wake up, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.55,0:04:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Boatdrift Ceremony...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Dad and {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} \Nhad told us it'd be useless,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was expecting something the whole time.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I told myself {\i1}something{\i0} would happen.{shortened; was 22 cps}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.73,0:05:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, something that terrible wound up happening.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.43,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you save Akari?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly happened that day?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.27,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd said that, after the Boatdrift Ceremony, you had something to tell me, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.97,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, even though I kept reaching for you, I couldn't get to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But never again.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you want me to, I'm never gonna let go of you again.{Never gonna give you up}{never gonna let you down}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Miuna{-chan} likes Hikari too.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.03,0:06:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so cute...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.96,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way she puts everything into caring for him and yet can't seem to take the next step.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I always thought of her as just a child,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.65,0:06:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she's the same age now \Nthat we were back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.33,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm almost the age that Akari{-san} was{ back then}.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You worried about that girl \Nfrom the sea village?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.81,0:06:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she'll wake up soon, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.92,0:06:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,she's lost her Ena.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She lost her Ena?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.03,0:06:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned that they found her sleeping in the graveyard of Wooden Maidens, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know something about all this?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.99,0:06:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more to the legend about the sea god and the Wooden Maiden.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,More to the legend?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.25,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many like to talk about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.97,0:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story with a sad ending.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't said much since you got back from the village.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.95,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Chisaki, \Nhow's Manaka doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had the chance to go see her.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said that there's \Nnothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.77,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now you two will have more data to sit on top of.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sit on top of"?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.01,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that neither Mihashi{-sensei} nor Tsumugu plan to announce their data
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.82,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,about our excursion into Shioshishio or about Miuna{-chan}'s Ena for quite some time.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mihashi{-sensei} plans to put it all \Ninto one research paper,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.65,0:08:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,at which point, he'll send it to an academic journal{ for review}, \Nand {then }officially present it once it's published.{Second comma to separate the "once it's published" from "submit it into an academic journal." Not really necessary, but meh.}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I agree with that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.85,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, Miuna{-chan}, and I didn't swim all the way to Shioshishio and put our lives in danger
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,just for the sake of your reputation.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a good reason for this, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If the paper isn't acknowledged by our peers,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll lose our research grants.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.78,0:08:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will put a stop to everything we've been working on...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.64,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}finding the link between the weather and Shioshishio, \Ntrying to prevent any more disasters—everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.03,0:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,By that point, the media will probably get involved and cause Miuna a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.01,0:08:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.41,0:08:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You never explain things without being asked first, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you give him a chance?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.13,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... there's a lot going on, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such an adult, Chisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for dinner.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, wai—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.67,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"An adult," huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This brings back memories!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You've gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.43,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.21,0:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... It's so small.{you think}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki, the bathwater's getting cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki, I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.95,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How long do you plan \Non staring, you idiots?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.21,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.75,0:11:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, don't sneak up on me like that.
