Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.58,Some Boring Chalk #59,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur0.8\c&H282C2E&\fscx43\fscy50\frz337.1\pos(1172.571,280.429)\b1}Marinated in Soy
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.58,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, I was just looking for Grandpa's plum wine.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a minor, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.81,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So what!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can drink some if I want!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.46,0:11:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm this lonely housewife who's suuuch an adult!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.75,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prepare it for you.
